from hudson paul hudson jr subject contradiction in mormonism there be a contradiction relate to the moral issue of polygamy in the mormon write in the book in the book of mormon call the book of jacob joseph smith write that it wa an abomination to god for david and solomon to have many wife later when joseph smith write the doctrine and covenant possibly when polygamy wa become an issue in hi personal life he write that it wa not an abomination for david to have many wife how do mormon answer thi contradiction link hudson 